{"tid":1448014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:20:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:35:37.000Z","uid":146558,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"7fe4f86112f1a74c8e9fa380bd5939b197c3a1af","tid":1448014,"uid":146558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:20:55.000Z","msg":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n出街流血 搭地鐵食tg照打 全部人唔好再係出面比狗咬 入機場"},{"pid":"09c604e85608b9a8d50856433d0bf8799c7e109c","tid":1448014,"uid":146558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:21:13.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"8b1baa6f7dd31ecacf0a0575f4850fda74503b6e","tid":1448014,"uid":146558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:21:23.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"a4d65ecdcb58039fe39c66fb4a844ff4100f3ff4","tid":1448014,"uid":146558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:21:33.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"643a8f38748e582f427b44e807da3740df24db1e","tid":1448014,"uid":146558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:21:43.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"6608a0ca82beeb4630ffc1d79f3c4a590480cee7","tid":1448014,"uid":146558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:21:53.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"d998c54972f0f00cc14f1fdf18e39bbd68e80f30","tid":1448014,"uid":146558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:22:03.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"27aa750db4cb6e948785139c99c8a2440e28b527","tid":1448014,"uid":23373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:22:05.000Z","msg":"其實有暗箭,點解要企出街比人打?<br />\n<br />\n入痕粉金粉麵粉蟲仔落信封，寄去所